1. *Glavom* smo odlučili da odemo na more. (We decided to go to the sea with our heads.)

2. Ne možemo da se spasemo *glavom*. (We can't escape with our heads.)

3. Ona sve vodi *glavom*. (She leads everything with her head.)

4. *Glavom* je izabrala da studira. (She chose to study with her head.)

5. Svi su nas pogledali *glavom*. (Everyone looked at us with their heads.)

6. *Glavom* je znao da se zaštiti. (He knew how to protect himself with his head.)